#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.76"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.76:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Yamakavagga"
msgstr "8. Pairs"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Dutiyasampadāsutta"
msgstr "76. Accomplishments (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.323"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhimā, bhikkhave, sampadā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these eight accomplishments."

msgctxt "an8.76:1.2"
msgid "Katamā aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.76:1.3"
msgid ""
"Uṭṭhānasampadā, ārakkhasampadā, kalyāṇamittatā, samajīvitā, saddhāsampadā, "
"sīlasampadā, cāgasampadā, paññāsampadā."
msgstr ""
"Accomplishment in initiative, protection, good friendship, and balanced "
"finances. And accomplishment in faith, ethics, generosity, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an8.76:1.4"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, uṭṭhānasampadā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in initiative?"

msgctxt "an8.76:1.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputto yena kammaṭṭhānena jīvitaṃ kappeti—"
msgstr "It’s when a respectable person earns a living by means such as"

msgctxt "an8.76:1.6"
msgid ""
"yadi kasiyā yadi vaṇijjāya yadi gorakkhena yadi issattena yadi rājaporisena "
"yadi sippaññatarena—"
msgstr ""
"farming, trade, raising cattle, archery, government service, or one of the "
"professions."

msgctxt "an8.76:1.7"
msgid ""
"tattha dakkho hoti analaso, tatrupāyāya vīmaṃsāya samannāgato, alaṃ kātuṃ "
"alaṃ saṃvidhātunti."
msgstr ""
"They understand how to go about these things in order to complete and "
"organize the work."

msgctxt "an8.76:1.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, uṭṭhānasampadā. (1)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in initiative."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, ārakkhasampadā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in protection?"

msgctxt "an8.76:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputtassa bhogā honti uṭṭhānavīriyādhigatā "
"bāhābalaparicitā sedāvakkhittā dhammikā dhammaladdhā te ārakkhena guttiyā "
"sampādeti:"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a respectable person owns legitimate wealth that he has earned by "
"his own efforts and initiative, built up with his own hands, gathered by the "
"sweat of the brow. They ensure it is guarded and protected, thinking:"

msgctxt "an8.76:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘kinti me bhoge neva rājāno hareyyuṃ, na corā hareyyuṃ, na aggi ḍaheyya, na "
"udakaṃ vaheyya, na appiyā dāyādā hareyyun’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘How can I prevent my wealth from being taken by rulers or bandits, consumed "
"by fire, swept away by flood, or taken by unloved heirs?’"

msgctxt "an8.76:2.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ārakkhasampadā. (2)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in protection."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, kalyāṇamittatā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in good friendship?"

msgctxt "an8.76:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputto yasmiṃ gāme vā nigame vā paṭivasati, tattha ye te "
"honti gahapatī vā gahapatiputtā vā daharā vā vuddhasīlino vuddhā vā "
"vuddhasīlino saddhāsampannā sīlasampannā cāgasampannā paññāsampannā, tehi "
"saddhiṃ santiṭṭhati sallapati sākacchaṃ samāpajjati; yathārūpānaṃ "
"saddhāsampannānaṃ saddhāsampadaṃ anusikkhati, yathārūpānaṃ sīlasampannānaṃ "
"sīlasampadaṃ anusikkhati, yathārūpānaṃ cāgasampannānaṃ cāgasampadaṃ "
"anusikkhati, yathārūpānaṃ paññāsampannānaṃ paññāsampadaṃ anusikkhati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a respectable person resides in a town or village. And in that "
"place there are householders or their children who may be young or old, but "
"are mature in conduct, accomplished in faith, ethics, generosity, and "
"wisdom. They associate with them, converse and engage in discussion. And "
"they emulate the same kind of accomplishment in faith, ethics, generosity, "
"and wisdom."

msgctxt "an8.76:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kalyāṇamittatā. (3)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in good friendship."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.324"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, samajīvitā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in balanced finances?"

msgctxt "an8.76:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputto āyañca bhogānaṃ viditvā vayañca bhogānaṃ viditvā "
"samaṃ jīvikaṃ kappeti nāccogāḷhaṃ nātihīnaṃ: ‘evaṃ me āyo vayaṃ pariyādāya "
"ṭhassati, na ca me vayo āyaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a respectable person, knowing their income and expenditure, "
"balances their finances, being neither too extravagant nor too frugal. They "
"think: ‘In this way my income will exceed my expenditure, not the reverse.’"

msgctxt "an8.76:4.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, tulādhāro vā tulādhārantevāsī vā tulaṃ paggahetvā "
"jānāti: ‘ettakena vā onataṃ, ettakena vā unnatan’ti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s like an appraiser or their apprentice who, holding up the scales, knows "
"that it’s low by this much or high by this much."

msgctxt "an8.76:4.4"
msgid ""
"evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, kulaputto āyañca bhogānaṃ viditvā vayañca bhogānaṃ "
"viditvā samaṃ jīvikaṃ kappeti nāccogāḷhaṃ nātihīnaṃ: ‘evaṃ me āyo vayaṃ "
"pariyādāya ṭhassati, na ca me vayo āyaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a respectable person, knowing their income and expenditure, "
"balances their finances, being neither too extravagant nor too frugal. They "
"think: ‘In this way my income will exceed my expenditure, not the reverse.’"

msgctxt "an8.76:4.5"
msgid ""
"Sacāyaṃ, bhikkhave, kulaputto appāyo samāno uḷāraṃ jīvikaṃ kappeti, tassa "
"bhavanti vattāro ‘udumbarakhādī vāyaṃ kulaputto bhoge khādatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"If a respectable person has little income but an opulent life, people will "
"say: ‘This respectable person eats their wealth like a fig-eater!’"

msgctxt "an8.76:4.6"
msgid ""
"Sace panāyaṃ, bhikkhave, kulaputto mahāyo samāno kasiraṃ jīvikaṃ kappeti, "
"tassa bhavanti vattāro: ‘ajeṭṭhamaraṇaṃ vāyaṃ kulaputto marissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"If a respectable person has a large income but a spartan life, people will "
"say: ‘This respectable person is starving themselves to death!’"

msgctxt "an8.76:4.7"
msgid ""
"Yato ca khoyaṃ, bhikkhave, kulaputto āyañca bhogānaṃ viditvā vayañca "
"bhogānaṃ viditvā samaṃ jīvikaṃ kappeti nāccogāḷhaṃ nātihīnaṃ: ‘evaṃ me āyo "
"vayaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati, na ca me vayo āyaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"But a respectable person, knowing their income and expenditure, leads a "
"balanced life, neither too extravagant nor too frugal, thinking: ‘In this "
"way my income will exceed my expenditure, not the reverse.’"

msgctxt "an8.76:4.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, samajīvitā. (4)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in balanced finances."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:5.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, saddhāsampadā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in faith?"

msgctxt "an8.76:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputto saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ:"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a respectable person has faith in the Realized One’s awakening:"

msgctxt "an8.76:5.3"
msgid "‘itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha … teacher of gods "
"and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "an8.76:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saddhāsampadā. (5)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in faith."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:6.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sīlasampadā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in ethics?"

msgctxt "an8.76:6.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputto pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a respectable person doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit "
"sexual misconduct, lie, or consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an8.76:6.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sīlasampadā. (6)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in ethics."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:7.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, cāgasampadā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in generosity?"

msgctxt "an8.76:7.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputto vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati … "
"pe … yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a respectable person lives at home rid of the stain of stinginess, "
"freely generous, open-handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving "
"to give and to share."

msgctxt "an8.76:7.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, cāgasampadā. (7)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in generosity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.325"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:8.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, paññāsampadā?"
msgstr "And what is accomplishment in wisdom?"

msgctxt "an8.76:8.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, kulaputto paññavā hoti … pe … sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a respectable person is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and "
"passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending "
"of suffering."

msgctxt "an8.76:8.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, paññāsampadā. (8)"
msgstr "This is called accomplishment in wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:9.1"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha sampadāti."
msgstr "These are the eight accomplishments."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:10.1"
msgid "Uṭṭhātā kammadheyyesu,"
msgstr "They’re enterprising in the workplace,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:10.2"
msgid "appamatto vidhānavā;"
msgstr "diligent in managing things,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:10.3"
msgid "Samaṃ kappeti jīvikaṃ,"
msgstr "they balance their finances,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:10.4"
msgid "sambhataṃ anurakkhati."
msgstr "and preserve their wealth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:11.1"
msgid "Saddho sīlena sampanno,"
msgstr "Faithful, accomplished in ethics,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:11.2"
msgid "vadaññū vītamaccharo;"
msgstr "kind, rid of stinginess,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:11.3"
msgid "Niccaṃ maggaṃ visodheti,"
msgstr "they always purify the path"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:11.4"
msgid "sotthānaṃ samparāyikaṃ."
msgstr "to well-being in lives to come."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:12.1"
msgid "Iccete aṭṭha dhammā ca,"
msgstr "And so these eight qualities"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:12.2"
msgid "saddhassa gharamesino;"
msgstr "of a faithful householder"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:12.3"
msgid "Akkhātā saccanāmena,"
msgstr "are declared by the one who is truly named"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:12.4"
msgid "ubhayattha sukhāvahā."
msgstr "to lead to happiness in both spheres,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an8.76:13.1"
msgid "Diṭṭhadhammahitatthāya,"
msgstr "welfare and benefit in this life,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:13.2"
msgid "samparāyasukhāya ca;"
msgstr "and happiness in the next."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:13.3"
msgid "Evametaṃ gahaṭṭhānaṃ,"
msgstr "This is how, for a householder,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.76:13.4"
msgid "cāgo puññaṃ pavaḍḍhatī”ti."
msgstr "merit grows by generosity.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.76:13.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
